   20: -module(overridden_bif_SUITE).
   21: -compile({no_auto_import,[is_reference/1,size/1]}).
   22: 
   23: -export([all/0, suite/0,groups/0,init_per_suite/1, end_per_suite/1,
   24: 	 init_per_group/2,end_per_group/2,
   25: 	 init_per_testcase/2,end_per_testcase/2,
   26: 	 overridden_bif/1]).
   27: 
   28: -include_lib("common_test/include/ct.hrl").
   29: 
   30: %% Used by overridden_bif/1.
   31: -import(gb_sets, [size/1]).
   32: -import(test_lib, [binary/1]).
   33: 
   34: suite() ->
   35:     [{ct_hooks,[ts_install_cth]},
   36:      {timetrap,{minutes,1}}].
   37: 
   38: all() ->
   39:     [overridden_bif].
   40: 
   41: groups() ->
   42:     [].
   43: 
   44: init_per_suite(Config) ->
   45:     test_lib:interpret(?MODULE),
   46:     Config.
   47: 
   48: end_per_suite(_Config) ->
   49:     ok.
   50: 
   51: init_per_group(_GroupName, Config) ->
   52:     Config.
   53: 
   54: end_per_group(_GroupName, Config) ->
   55:     Config.
   56: 
   57: 
   58: init_per_testcase(Case, Config) when is_atom(Case), is_list(Config) ->
   59:     Config.
   60: 
   61: end_per_testcase(Case, Config) when is_atom(Case), is_list(Config) ->
   62:     ok.
   63: 
   64: overridden_bif(_Config) ->
   65:     L = [-3,-2,-1,0,1,2,3,4],
   66:     [-3,0,3] = do_overridden_bif_1(L),
   67:     [-2,0,2,4] = do_overridden_bif_2(L),
   68:     [3] = do_overridden_bif_3(L),
   69:     [2,4] = do_overridden_bif_4(L),
   70: 
   71:     Set = gb_sets:from_list(L),
   72:     [Set] = do_overridden_bif_5([gb_sets:singleton(42),Set]),
   73: 
   74:     [100,0] = do_overridden_bif_6([100|L]),
   75:     ok.
   76: 
   77: do_overridden_bif_1(L) ->
   78:     [E || E <- L, is_reference(E)].
   79: 
   80: do_overridden_bif_2(L) ->
   81:     [E || E <- L, port(E)].
   82: 
   83: do_overridden_bif_3(L) ->
   84:     [E || E <- L, (is_reference(E) andalso E > 0)].
   85: 
   86: do_overridden_bif_4(L) ->
   87:     [E || E <- L, (port(E) andalso E > 0)].
   88: 
   89: do_overridden_bif_5(L) ->
   90:     [E || E <- L, size(E) > 1].
   91: 
   92: do_overridden_bif_6(L) ->
   93:     [E || E <- L, binary(E)].
   94: 
   95: is_reference(N) ->
   96:     N rem 3 =:= 0.
   97: 
   98: port(N) ->
   99:     N rem 2 =:= 0.
